Installation Guide
Prerequisites
‚Ä¢	Android Studio installed on your system.
‚Ä¢	Minimum SDK version: 21 (Android 5.0 Lollipop).
‚Ä¢	Recommended device: Android smartphone with at least 2GB RAM.

Usage
1.	Launch the App: Open the BMI Calculator on your Android device.
2.	Input Your Details:
o	Enter your height and weight in the respective fields.
o	Select units (metric or imperial) based on your preference.
3.	View Results: The app instantly calculates and displays your BMI value along with the corresponding health category.
4.	Explore Suggestions: Read health tips and guidelines tailored to your BMI category.
